The Cambridges released a heartfelt post for the youngster's birthday alongside a sweet snap which gave a hint as to where the family had headed on their holiday. The photo, which showed a smiling George in a pale blue polo shirt, revealed the family were enjoying a UK beach getaway. Earlier this month, and just days after the kids broke up from school, the royals were seen embarking on their private jet alongside their pet pooch Orla. Kate, 40, appeared to be wearing a white summer dress and the same straw hat she donned at Wimbledon to watch the Ladies' Singles Final.   FOLLOW FOR MORE LIVE UPDATES..